95
00:11:50,370 --> 00:11:53,390
<b>they saved up some money to go on a trip together someday.</b>

96
00:11:53,570 --> 00:11:56,570
<b>They go on a trip after they break up? Together?</b>

97
00:11:56,570 --> 00:11:58,030
<b>No, separately.</b>

98
00:11:58,130 --> 00:11:59,440
<b>Really?</b>

99
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:02,170
<b>And then? What happens?</b>

100
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:07,250
<b>I did my very best.</b>

101
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:14,590
<b>But why now?</b>

102
00:12:15,190 --> 00:12:18,150
<b>You never acted on it, so why now? Why this way?</b>

103
00:12:18,150 --> 00:12:20,390
<b>Because I couldn't win his heart no matter how hard I tried.</b>

104
00:12:22,760 --> 00:12:26,570
<b>I just couldn't make it happen. What was I supposed to do?</b>

105
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:28,100
<b>You see,</b>

106
00:12:29,870 --> 00:12:32,030
<b>I actually had a crush on you.</b>

107
00:12:33,980 --> 00:12:35,030
<b>What?</b>

108
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:38,450
<b>For a very long time.</b>

109
00:12:41,170 --> 00:12:42,320
<b>I didn't know.</b>

110
00:12:44,040 --> 00:12:45,960
<b>What if you knew, Eun Seop?</b>

111
00:12:51,330 --> 00:12:52,790
<b>Nothing...</b>

112
00:12:54,500 --> 00:12:56,420
<b>would've changed.</b>

113
00:13:01,660 --> 00:13:04,000
<b>- Hey. - I didn't get into any colleges.</b>

114
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:06,370
<b>- Gosh. - You can try again next year.</b>

115
00:13:13,950 --> 00:13:16,540
<b>- Hey. - Do you want to do this with me?</b>

116
00:13:16,540 --> 00:13:17,720
<b>Hey, Eun Seop!</b>

117
00:13:18,140 --> 00:13:19,650
<b>- Hey, come on. - No.</b>

118
00:13:19,650 --> 00:13:22,250
<b>You can have this. I got too many. Come, I'll buy you jjajangmyeon.</b>

119
00:13:22,250 --> 00:13:25,020
<b>Come on. Everyone's waiting. Hurry.</b>

120
00:13:25,020 --> 00:13:26,890
<b>Hey, come on. Quick.</b>

121
00:13:28,230 --> 00:13:30,290
<b>- Right? - Oh, gosh!</b>

122
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:34,870
<b>Sure, I may have had many chances, but so what?</b>

123
00:13:37,630 --> 00:13:40,240
<b>The timing was always off.</b>

124
00:13:44,210 --> 00:13:46,980
<b>As if I shouldn't exist in his life.</b>

125
00:14:09,160 --> 00:14:12,340
<b>Eun Seop! Lim Eun Seop!</b>

126
00:14:12,530 --> 00:14:14,770
<b>You said you'd buy me a gaming console with your savings.</b>

127
00:14:14,770 --> 00:14:16,900
<b>- Did you bring it? - Yes, it's in my backpack.</b>

128
00:14:16,900 --> 00:14:18,770
<b>Oh, nice!</b>

129
00:14:18,770 --> 00:14:20,170
<b>Girls, say hi. This is my brother.</b>

130
00:14:20,170 --> 00:14:22,040
