137
00:14:53,140 --> 00:14:54,870
<b>The one who used to live in the mountains.</b>

138
00:14:58,640 --> 00:15:00,550
<b>All right, let's go!</b>

139
00:15:00,550 --> 00:15:01,690
<b>Okay.</b>

140
00:15:08,790 --> 00:15:10,920
