142
00:15:24,370 --> 00:15:26,620
<b>That's why I couldn't do anything.</b>

143
00:15:29,320 --> 00:15:30,450
<b>I couldn't talk to him...</b>

144
00:15:31,120 --> 00:15:33,120
<b>or even call him once.</b>

145
00:15:37,550 --> 00:15:39,700
<b>But I suddenly became brave...</b>

146
00:15:41,150 --> 00:15:42,600
<b>after you came.</b>

147
00:15:44,330 --> 00:15:45,390
<b>What?</b>

148
00:15:45,740 --> 00:15:47,470
<b>After you came here,</b>

149
00:15:48,100 --> 00:15:51,070
<b>I suddenly became anxious and determined.</b>

150
00:15:51,530 --> 00:15:54,580
<b>I wanted to get in your way and be mean to you.</b>

151
00:15:55,540 --> 00:15:56,750
<b>What did you say?</b>

152
00:15:58,210 --> 00:15:59,750
<b>Be honest.</b>

153
00:16:00,750 --> 00:16:03,250
<b>There was a time when you intentionally got in my way.</b>

154
00:16:40,280 --> 00:16:42,860
<b>Hey, Bo Yeong!</b>

155
00:16:44,190 --> 00:16:46,960
<b>Hey, why are you crying?</b>

156
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:49,020
<b>Why are you crying? Did something happen?</b>

157
00:16:49,020 --> 00:16:52,530
<b>Because of what happened in the AV room earlier, right?</b>

158
00:16:53,700 --> 00:16:55,840
<b>Mok Hae Won made a move on Lim Eun Seop, didn't she?</b>

159
00:16:56,840 --> 00:17:00,340
<b>Gosh, I never liked that girl.</b>

160
00:17:00,340 --> 00:17:02,380
<b>That sneaky girl.</b>

161
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:04,650
<b>Gosh, how dare she?</b>

162
00:17:06,270 --> 00:17:07,480
<b>No, never.</b>

163
00:17:08,570 --> 00:17:11,190
