164
00:17:11,310 --> 00:17:12,750
<b>Not even once.</b>

165
00:17:14,110 --> 00:17:16,660
<b>You never made a move on him deliberately,</b>

166
00:17:16,890 --> 00:17:19,460
<b>knowing that I had a crush on him?</b>

167
00:17:19,460 --> 00:17:20,820
<b>No, never.</b>

168
00:17:21,930 --> 00:17:24,630
<b>I speculated that you probably liked him,</b>

169
00:17:24,630 --> 00:17:27,060
<b>but I didn't know that Eun Seop was your crush.</b>

170
00:17:27,940 --> 00:17:29,600
<b>You know what?</b>

171
00:17:31,140 --> 00:17:33,100
<b>I have a crush on someone.</b>

