174
00:17:44,720 --> 00:17:47,350
<b>That's why I can't understand you at all.</b>

175
00:17:48,080 --> 00:17:51,050
<b>Why would you become so mean because of me?</b>

176
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:55,050
<b>Bo Yeong.</b>

177
00:17:56,790 --> 00:17:59,970
