178
00:18:14,540 --> 00:18:15,540
<b>Yes.</b>

179
00:18:16,840 --> 00:18:17,990
<b>I found her.</b>

180
00:18:19,510 --> 00:18:22,250
<b>No, don't worry. I'll bring her down.</b>

181
00:18:22,930 --> 00:18:23,930
<b>Okay.</b>

182
00:18:30,630 --> 00:18:32,400
<b>Follow me, and don't fall behind.</b>

183
00:19:07,470 --> 00:19:08,830
<b>Out of the way.</b>

184
00:19:08,830 --> 00:19:11,000
