185
00:19:20,040 --> 00:19:21,040
<b>What?</b>

186
00:19:22,070 --> 00:19:23,340
<b>Do you need anything?</b>

187
00:19:23,340 --> 00:19:25,220
<b>Just tell me the terms of the deal.</b>

188
00:19:25,220 --> 00:19:28,390
<b>Oh, right. I was supposed to tell you that.</b>

189
00:19:37,260 --> 00:19:39,090
<b>What? You don't like it?</b>

190
00:19:39,090 --> 00:19:41,670
