194
00:20:23,150 --> 00:20:24,340
<b>Thank you.</b>

195
00:20:30,990 --> 00:20:34,350
<b>I hear you're seeing Shim Myeong Yeo these days.</b>

196
00:20:35,160 --> 00:20:36,160
<b>Yes.</b>

197
00:20:39,130 --> 00:20:41,730
<b>And she's holed up in the woods somewhere in Gangwon Province?</b>

198
00:20:45,970 --> 00:20:50,470
<b>You know, I want you to focus on me...</b>

199
00:20:51,170 --> 00:20:52,910
<b>whether it's as a writer...</b>

200
00:20:53,910 --> 00:20:54,910
<b>or as a woman.</b>

201
00:20:56,570 --> 00:20:59,340
