203
00:21:03,250 --> 00:21:05,040
<b>Her book will be published...</b>

204
00:21:05,040 --> 00:21:06,920
<b>whether you see her or not.</b>

205
00:21:07,350 --> 00:21:09,250
<b>So just publish her book...</b>

206
00:21:09,250 --> 00:21:10,820
<b>without seeing her.</b>

207
00:21:11,350 --> 00:21:13,930
<b>Okay? Can you do that?</b>

208
00:21:16,470 --> 00:21:18,560
<b>It's all true, Yun Taek.</b>

209
00:21:21,530 --> 00:21:23,970
