221
00:21:51,430 --> 00:21:52,970
<b>What did they say?</b>

222
00:21:52,970 --> 00:21:55,440
<b>Everything people say about me is true.</b>

223
00:21:55,440 --> 00:21:56,440
<b>Right.</b>

224
00:21:56,670 --> 00:21:57,910
<b>That's the truth.</b>

225
00:22:00,480 --> 00:22:04,000
<b>They say she had a fling with her brother-in-law,</b>

226
00:22:04,910 --> 00:22:08,180
<b>and that's why her sister killed her husband.</b>

227
00:22:10,810 --> 00:22:12,190
<b>Believe what they say.</b>

228
00:22:17,130 --> 00:22:18,820
<b>So you didn't know?</b>

229
00:22:19,630 --> 00:22:23,900
<b>Then why did you two break up?</b>

230
00:22:24,320 --> 00:22:25,320
<b>Gosh, it's hot.</b>

231
00:22:26,440 --> 00:22:29,800
<b>Excuse me. I asked for water, not broth.</b>

232
