<b>Cha Yun Taek.</b>

234
00:22:34,380 --> 00:22:35,380
<b>Cha...</b>

235
00:22:37,840 --> 00:22:38,840
<b>Myeong Yeo!</b>

236
00:22:39,650 --> 00:22:40,650
<b>Myeong Yeo!</b>

237
00:22:43,750 --> 00:22:44,920
<b>Answer me.</b>

238
00:22:46,810 --> 00:22:48,110
<b>You're very persistent.</b>

239
00:22:49,160 --> 00:22:51,320
<b>Just tell me the reason.</b>

240
00:22:51,660 --> 00:22:52,850
<b>Is that so hard?</b>

241
00:22:53,520 --> 00:22:54,520
<b>Yun Taek.</b>

242
00:22:57,200 --> 00:22:58,320
<b>Have a good life.</b>

243
00:23:00,240 --> 00:23:01,740
<b>Have a good life.</b>

244
00:23:02,090 --> 00:23:03,300
<b>Get married like you've always wanted,</b>

245
00:23:03,300 --> 00:23:04,530
<b>have kids like you've always dreamed of,</b>

246
00:23:04,530 --> 00:23:06,680
<b>and live happily ever after.</b>

247
00:23:08,100 --> 00:23:10,100
<b>Myeong Yeo.</b>

248
00:23:10,980 --> 00:23:14,010
<b>Please be happy. Forget an idiot like me, okay?</b>

249
00:23:14,720 --> 00:23:17,310
<b>Myeong Yeo.</b>

250
00:23:17,650 --> 00:23:18,810
<b>Let go!</b>

251
00:23:26,290 --> 00:23:28,200
<b>I'm going to do everything with you.</b>

252
00:23:33,670 --> 00:23:35,400
<b>I'm going to do everything with you.</b>

253
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:42,500
<b>Like this.</b>

254
00:24:06,530 --> 00:24:07,530
<b>I'm...</b>

255
00:24:09,030 --> 00:24:10,030
<b>not.</b>

256
00:24:29,580 --> 00:24:32,230
<b>Everything people say about me is true.</b>

257
00:24:32,700 --> 00:24:33,930
<b>That's the truth.</b>

258
00:24:36,590 --> 00:24:38,000
<b>Believe what they say.</b>

259
00:26:15,250 --> 00:26:16,750
<b>- Hae Won. - You woke up?</b>

260
00:26:16,750 --> 00:26:17,750
<b>Yes.</b>

261
00:26:18,220 --> 00:26:21,160
<b>Are you feeling okay?</b>

262
00:26:21,160 --> 00:26:22,620
<b>You didn't catch a cold or anything?</b>

263
00:26:22,620 --> 00:26:23,890
<b>No, I didn't.</b>

264
00:26:24,490 --> 00:26:25,590
<b>How are you?</b>

265
00:26:25,860 --> 00:26:26,960
<b>I'm good.</b>

266
00:26:29,360 --> 00:26:31,730
<b>Did you talk to...</b>

267
00:26:32,100 --> 00:26:33,440
<b>- Did it... - It went well.</b>

268
00:26:34,770 --> 00:26:35,900
<b>That's great.</b>

269
00:26:40,380 --> 00:26:44,180
<b>What? Don't tell me you're sleepy again.</b>

270
00:26:44,410 --> 00:26:45,650
<b>I am.</b>

271
00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:50,350
<b>I thought you had insomnia. Or was it mythomania?</b>

272
00:26:50,350 --> 00:26:52,290
<b>- I do. - You have mythomania?</b>

273
00:26:52,290 --> 00:26:54,190
<b>No, I have insomnia.</b>

274
00:26:57,960 --> 00:27:00,700
<b>No, you can't fall asleep now. Get up.</b>

275
00:27:00,700 --> 00:27:02,200
<b>- Hae Won. - What?</b>

276
00:27:02,200 --> 00:27:03,570
<b>Let me take a short nap.</b>

277
00:27:03,570 --> 00:27:04,970
<b>What short nap?</b>

278
00:27:04,970 --> 00:27:07,070
<b>You slept all this time. Get up already.</b>

279
00:27:07,070 --> 00:27:08,870
<b>I'm bored. Come on.</b>

280
00:27:08,870 --> 00:27:09,940
<b>What?</b>

281
00:27:10,340 --> 00:27:11,370
<b>Hey.</b>

282
00:27:12,610 --> 00:27:13,680
<b>Hey.</b>

283
00:27:15,040 --> 00:27:16,580
<b>- Get up. - What?</b>

284
00:27:17,010 --> 00:27:18,150
<b>My eyes.</b>

285
00:27:19,480 --> 00:27:21,150
<b>Come on, get up.</b>

286
00:27:21,250 --> 00:27:23,990
<b>Get up. Come on, get up.</b>

287
00:27:24,820 --> 00:27:25,920
<b>- Hey. - Get up.</b>

288
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:27,120
<b>I'm going to make you into the Joker.</b>

289
00:27:27,120 --> 00:27:28,790
<b>Okay, I'll get up.</b>

290
00:27:30,090 --> 00:27:33,000
<b>Hey, no! Get up.</b>

291
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:34,960
<b>You're really not going to get up? Come on.</b>

292
00:27:34,960 --> 00:27:36,700
<b>Hey! Get up.</b>

293
00:27:42,070 --> 00:27:43,070
<b>Oh, boy.</b>

294
00:27:44,940 --> 00:27:46,010
<b>- Hello, Eun Sil. - What?</b>

295
00:27:46,110 --> 00:27:49,010
<b>- What a very casual entrance. - Wasn't it?</b>

296
00:27:49,210 --> 00:27:52,580
<b>Gosh, our timing is finally right for a change.</b>

297
00:27:52,580 --> 00:27:53,650
<b>I know.</b>

298
00:27:55,520 --> 00:27:57,420
<b>Look at those roses.</b>

299
00:27:59,820 --> 00:28:01,790
<b>Hey. Aren't these...</b>

300
00:28:01,790 --> 00:28:04,360
<b>the same ones you gave me a long time ago?</b>

301
00:28:04,860 --> 00:28:05,930
<b>What?</b>

302
00:28:08,200 --> 00:28:09,260
<b>What...</b>

303
00:28:09,830 --> 00:28:11,730
<b>Are you asking me out like this?</b>

304
00:28:12,070 --> 00:28:13,140
<b>Yes.</b>

305
00:28:13,270 --> 00:28:16,170
<b>I'm Lee Jang Woo, the student body president.</b>

306
00:28:16,170 --> 00:28:19,270
<b>- I know that you're Lee Jang Woo. - You know me?</b>

307
00:28:20,040 --> 00:28:21,480
<b>Those roses are white.</b>

308
00:28:21,780 --> 00:28:25,980
<b>You must be very kind and innocent, right?</b>

309
00:28:25,980 --> 00:28:27,050
<b>Yes, I am.</b>

310
00:28:27,750 --> 00:28:29,220
<b>But that's too bad.</b>

311
00:28:29,220 --> 00:28:33,290
<b>Baek Gyeong asked me out during lunch earlier today.</b>

312
00:28:33,690 --> 00:28:34,990
<b>And I said yes.</b>

313
00:28:35,360 --> 00:28:36,360
<b>What?</b>

314
00:28:36,830 --> 00:28:37,930
<b>Sorry.</b>

315
00:28:39,660 --> 00:28:42,130
<b>- I guess our timing didn't match. - Timing?</b>

316
00:28:43,430 --> 00:28:46,230
<b>- What is that? - It's nothing.</b>

317
00:28:46,440 --> 00:28:48,240
<b>- Can I read it? - No, you can't. Why?</b>

318
00:28:48,270 --> 00:28:50,540
<b>Don't take it. Put that back down. Why?</b>

319
00:28:51,040 --> 00:28:53,240
<b>- Thank you. - But that's not for you. Why?</b>

320
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:55,480
<b>- Put that back down. - But I'll have to say no.</b>

321
00:28:55,480 --> 00:28:57,610
<b>- I said no. - What?</b>

322
00:28:58,180 --> 00:28:59,880
<b>Guys, I said no, okay?</b>

323
00:28:59,880 --> 00:29:01,880
<b>Eun Sil, that letter... Eun Sil, the letter!</b>

324
00:29:01,880 --> 00:29:04,420
<b>- Give me the letter. Eun Sil! - He got rejected.</b>

325
00:29:04,420 --> 00:29:08,120
<b>- He got rejected! - She said no!</b>

326
00:29:08,120 --> 00:29:10,160
<b>When did you guys come?</b>

327
00:29:10,160 --> 00:29:12,530
<b>- She said no. - How embarrassing.</b>

328
00:29:12,530 --> 00:29:15,300
<b>- Where are you going? - He got rejected!</b>

329
00:29:16,700 --> 00:29:17,830
<b>Then...</b>

330
00:29:18,430 --> 00:29:20,570
<b>if you didn't go out with Baek Gyeong back then...</b>

331
00:29:20,570 --> 00:29:22,400
<b>- Of course, I would've said no. - Right?</b>

332
00:29:22,400 --> 00:29:25,740
<b>Yes. You weren't my type back then. Not at all.</b>

333
00:29:25,740 --> 00:29:29,640
<b>I was attracted to bad boys back then.</b>

334
00:29:29,640 --> 00:29:31,010
<b>Bad boys?</b>

335
00:29:31,010 --> 00:29:33,280
<b>I guess Baek Gyeong was kind of bad.</b>

336
00:29:33,380 --> 00:29:35,280
<b>I heard you're going somewhere nice later.</b>

337
00:29:35,380 --> 00:29:37,750
<b>- Somewhere nice? - Yes, I'm going to follow you.</b>

338
00:29:37,750 --> 00:29:39,190
<b>It's going to be fun.</b>

339
00:29:39,520 --> 00:29:41,060
<b>Follow me where?</b>

340
00:29:41,060 --> 00:29:45,430
<b>I've already put in a word, okay?</b>

341
00:29:48,060 --> 00:29:50,000
<b>Eun Sil? Eun Sil.</b>

342
00:29:50,930 --> 00:29:52,700
<b>- Eun Sil. - Hey!</b>

343
00:29:52,700 --> 00:29:53,900
<b>Hi, Ji Young.</b>

344
00:29:53,900 --> 00:29:56,100
<b>- Hello. - Hey, you can have some too.</b>

345
00:29:56,100 --> 00:29:58,340
<b>- It's all right. - Okay.</b>

346
00:29:58,440 --> 00:30:00,480
<b>- I'm here. - Hi, come in.</b>

347
00:30:00,480 --> 00:30:02,740
<b>This radish water kimchi is perfectly ripe and delicious.</b>

348
00:30:02,740 --> 00:30:05,580
<b>- Goodness, that looks good. - Come try some.</b>

349
00:30:05,580 --> 00:30:07,850
<b>- Thank you so much. - Sure.</b>

350
00:30:07,850 --> 00:30:10,850
<b>It's so warm in here. Can you make me some sesame oil?</b>

351
00:30:10,850 --> 00:30:13,160
<b>Okay, I'll make it, so come pick it up tomorrow.</b>

352
00:30:13,160 --> 00:30:14,760
<b>Okay, thanks.</b>

353
00:30:14,860 --> 00:30:17,590
<b>By the way, did you hear?</b>

354
00:30:17,590 --> 00:30:19,130
<b>Hear what?</b>

355
00:30:19,130 --> 00:30:21,630
<b>The daughter of Hodu House came here.</b>

356
00:30:21,630 --> 00:30:23,900
<b>The daughter of that family always lived there.</b>

357
00:30:23,900 --> 00:30:25,370
<b>No, not her.</b>

358
00:30:25,470 --> 00:30:27,740
<b>You know, the daughter...</b>

359
00:30:30,170 --> 00:30:32,970
<b>You know, the daughter who killed her husband.</b>

360
00:30:33,880 --> 00:30:35,410
<b>Can you believe it?</b>

361
00:30:35,410 --> 00:30:38,210
<b>How can she come back here after doing that to her husband?</b>

362
00:30:38,210 --> 00:30:41,280
<b>Well, the women from that family are all so spiteful.</b>

363
00:30:41,280 --> 00:30:43,590
<b>Even their mom was spiteful.</b>

364
00:30:43,590 --> 00:30:46,660
<b>Both her daughters were just like her.</b>

365
00:30:46,660 --> 00:30:49,790
<b>How spiteful could one be to kill her own husband...</b>

366
00:30:51,260 --> 00:30:55,230
<b>Right, weren't you close with her granddaughter?</b>

367
00:30:55,700 --> 00:30:58,130
<b>Bo Yeong, what are you doing? Go to your room.</b>

368
00:30:58,130 --> 00:31:01,570
<b>No, I need to go to the academy. Bye.</b>

369
00:31:15,520 --> 00:31:16,720
<b>You promised me...</b>

370
00:31:17,620 --> 00:31:21,290
<b>not to tell anyone either.</b>

371
00:31:24,560 --> 00:31:26,230
<b>I trusted Joo Hee.</b>

372
00:31:26,230 --> 00:31:28,130
<b>And I trusted you.</b>

373
